### Station API Tests

@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000/api

### Test 1: Get all stations
GET {{baseUrl}}/stations

### Test 2: Get stations with IATA filter
GET {{baseUrl}}/stations?iata=BUD

### Test 3: Get stations with IATA filter (case insensitive)
GET {{baseUrl}}/stations?iata=ltn

### Test 4: Get stations with name filter (partial match)
GET {{baseUrl}}/stations?name=London

### Test 5: Get stations with name filter (full match)
GET {{baseUrl}}/stations?name=Budapest

### Test 6: Get stations with name filter (case insensitive)
GET {{baseUrl}}/stations?name=london

### Test 7: Get stations that have connection to specific airport
GET {{baseUrl}}/stations?hasConnection=BUD

### Test 8: Get stations that have connection to LTN
GET {{baseUrl}}/stations?hasConnection=LTN

### Test 9: Complex filter - stations with "Rome" in name
GET {{baseUrl}}/stations?name=Rome

### Test 10: Get specific station by IATA code (BUD)
GET {{baseUrl}}/stations/BUD

### Test 11: Get specific station by IATA code (LTN)
GET {{baseUrl}}/stations/LTN

### Test 12: Get specific station by IATA code (case insensitive)
GET {{baseUrl}}/stations/bud

### Test 13: Get specific station by IATA code (non-existent)
GET {{baseUrl}}/stations/XYZ

### Test 14: Get connections for BUD station
GET {{baseUrl}}/stations/BUD/connections

### Test 15: Get connections for LTN station
GET {{baseUrl}}/stations/LTN/connections

### Test 16: Get connections for non-existent station
GET {{baseUrl}}/stations/XYZ/connections

### Test 17: Search stations by name - "London"
GET {{baseUrl}}/stations/search/London

### Test 18: Search stations by name - "Paris"
GET {{baseUrl}}/stations/search/Paris

### Test 19: Search stations by name - partial match "Rom"
GET {{baseUrl}}/stations/search/Rom

### Test 20: Search stations by name - case insensitive "budapest"
GET {{baseUrl}}/stations/search/budapest

### Test 21: Search stations by name - non-existent
GET {{baseUrl}}/stations/search/NonExistent
